com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Class JSObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.JSValue
      • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.JSObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JSArray, JSBooleanObject, JSFunction, JSNumberObject, JSStringObject 

    public class JSObject
extends JSValue
    Represents a JavaScript object. Provides access to the object's properties and functions. JavaScript object is alive until its JavaScript execution context exist. Once execution context is disposed, all JavaScript objects available in scope of this context will be automatically disposed. If you try to access already disposed object, you will get IllegalStateException.
    表示一个JavaScript对象。提供对对象的属性和功能的访问。在存在JavaScript执行上下文之前，JavaScript对象一直处于活动状态。处置执行上下文后，将自动处置该上下文范围内可用的所有JavaScript对象。如果尝试访问已处置的对象，则将得到IllegalStateException。

      • setProperty

        public boolean setProperty(java.lang.String name,
                           java.lang.Object value)
        Sets a new property with the given name or modifies existing one in the current JavaScript object and returns true if the property with the given name was created or updated successfully.

        The name parameter represents JavaScript object's property name. Via the property name you can access its value. The value can be one of the following types: String, Boolean, Integer, Long, Short, Byte, Double, Float, Object[], int, boolean, long, short, byte, double, float, Object, JSONString, JSFunctionCallback.

        As a property value you can set an instance of java.lang.Object type. In this case the Java object will be automatically converted/wrapped into JavaScript object. You can access and invoke all Java object's public methods and fields (including the inherited ones) directly from JavaScript code.

        Important security note: injecting Java objects is a powerful feature that might present a security risk for your application. JavaScript code can access public fields and methods of the injected Java object including Java Reflection API (e.g. Object.getClass() method). An untrusted JavaScript code on the loaded web page could allow an attacker to execute any Java code with permissions of Java process. For example, if you inject File object into JavaScript code, JavaScript will get access to the local file system.

        使用给定名称设置新属性或修改当前JavaScript对象中的现有属性，如果具有给定名称的属性已成功创建或更新，则返回true。 name参数表示JavaScript对象的属性名称。通过属性名称，您可以访问其值。该值可以是以下类型之一：字符串，布尔值，整数，长整数，短整数，字节，双精度，浮点数，对象[]，整数，布尔值，长整数，短整数，字节，双精度数，浮点数，对象，JSONString，JSFunctionCallback。作为属性值，您可以设置java.lang.Object类型的实例。在这种情况下，Java对象将自动转换/包装为JavaScript对象。您可以直接从JavaScript代码访问和调用所有Java对象的公共方法和字段（包括继承的）。重要的安全说明：注入Java对象是一项强大的功能，可能会给您的应用程序带来安全风险。 JavaScript代码可以访问注入的Java对象的公共字段和方法，包括Java Reflection API（例如Object.getClass（）方法）。加载的网页上不受信任的JavaScript代码可能使攻击者能够在Java进程的许可下执行任何Java代码。例如，如果将File对象注入JavaScript代码，则JavaScript将可以访问本地文件系统。
        Parameters:
        name - string that represents name of the property. Cannot be null or empty. -代表属性名称的字符串。不能为空。
        value - a new value associated with the property with the given name. Cannot be null or JSObject with a different JavaScript context. -与具有给定的属性相关联的新值。不能为或具有其他JavaScript上下文。
        Returns:
        true when property with name was created or updated successfully. 创建或更新属性成功的时间。
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when name is null or empty.
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when value is null or represents JSObject with a different JavaScript context.
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - when object is already disposed or invalid.
